flowchart TD
  A[Repo Skeleton<br/>README + .gitignore + pinned env] --> B[Ingestion Module<br/>scripts/ingest_lfw.py]
  B --> C[Manifest Artifact<br/>outputs/manifest.(json|yaml)]
  B --> D[Samples Table Artifact<br/>outputs/lfw_samples.(csv|jsonl)]
  D --> E[Pair Generation Module<br/>scripts/make_pairs.py]
  E --> F[Pair Files (Saved Splits)<br/>outputs/pairs/train.*<br/>outputs/pairs/val.*<br/>outputs/pairs/test.*]
  F --> G[Similarity Module<br/>src/similarity.py]
  G --> H[Benchmark Module<br/>scripts/bench_similarity.py]
  H --> I[Benchmark Results Artifact<br/>outputs/bench/* or console output]
  I --> J[Clean Clone Repro Test<br/>(manual checklist)]
  J --> K[Git Tag Release<br/>v0.1 points to reproducible commit]

  subgraph RepoStructure[Required Project Structure]
    A1[src/<br/>importable code]:::box
    A2[scripts/<br/>CLI entrypoints]:::box
    A3[configs/<br/>seed, split policy, pair policy, paths]:::box
    A4[tests/<br/>light tests + determinism checks]:::box
    A5[notebooks/<br/>optional sanity]:::box
    A6[data/<br/>dataset cache, NOT committed]:::warn
    A7[outputs/<br/>generated artifacts, usually NOT committed]:::warn
  end

  A --> RepoStructure

  subgraph IngestionDetails[Ingestion: What it Must Guarantee]
    B1[Download/Load LFW (TFDS or other)] --> B2[Deterministic ordering<br/>(e.g., sort identities; stable sample IDs)]
    B2 --> B3[Deterministic split policy<br/>(identity-level OR image-level; fixed seed)]
    B3 --> B4[Write manifest incl.<br/>seed + split_policy + counts + data_source + cache dir]
  end
  B --> IngestionDetails

  subgraph PairDetails[Pair Generation: What it Must Guarantee]
    E1[Read samples table + split assignments] --> E2[Define pair policy<br/>(#pos/#neg; sampling rules)]
    E2 --> E3[Seeded sampling + sorted candidate lists]
    E3 --> E4[Write pair files per split<br/>(left_ref, right_ref, label, split)]
    E4 --> E5[Rerun determinism check<br/>(identical files)]
  end
  E --> PairDetails

  subgraph SimilarityDetails[Similarity + Benchmark: What it Must Guarantee]
    G1[Vectorized cosine similarity<br/>Input: (N,D)+(N,D) -> (N,)] --> G2[Vectorized euclidean distance<br/>Input: (N,D)+(N,D) -> (N,)]
    G2 --> H1[Benchmark loop vs vectorized<br/>time.perf_counter or similar]
    H1 --> H2[Correctness check<br/>allclose + max abs diff tolerance]
  end
  G --> SimilarityDetails

  subgraph ReproDetails[Reproducibility: What TA Will Do]
    J1[Fresh clone] --> J2[Create env from pinned requirements]
    J2 --> J3[Run README commands: ingest -> pairs -> bench]
    J3 --> J4[Verify outputs exist + reruns identical]
    J4 --> K1[Checkout tag v0.1 and repeat]
  end
  J --> ReproDetails

  classDef box fill:#eef,stroke:#336,stroke-width:1px,color:#000;
  classDef warn fill:#ffecec,stroke:#a33,stroke-width:1px,color:#000;